---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About"
	description="A short introduction to this blog."
	pubDate={new Date('July 01 2026')}
>
	<p>
		This is my personal blog, a place to keep technical notes and things I&rsquo;m
		learning along the way.
	</p>
	<p>
		Most posts focus on frontend and JavaScript topics. I try to keep them short so I can
		come back and expand on them later.
	</p>
	<p>
		The site is built with Astro, content is written in Markdown, and the interface leans on
		a minimal pixel-art style so the reading experience stays out of the way.
	</p>
</Layout>
